description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Mont Saint-Michel
-Vue de nuit de Colmar (Night view of Colmar)
-Château de Versailles (Palace of Versailles)
-Annecy
-Gordes
-Pont du Gard
-Strasbourg
-La tour Eiffel (Eiffel Tower)
-Cathédrale Notre-Dame de Paris (Notre-Dame de Paris)
-Béziers
name: France - Most beautiful places in the World -
